  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK217">
<l>maruntākit tappā marattaṟṟāṟ celvam</l>
<l>peruntakai yāṉkaṭ paṭiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If wealth be in the possession of a man who has the great excellence (of benevolence), it is like a tree which as a medicine is an infallible cure for disease.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
